{"tid":1370721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[真相還原] 機場連儂人 請廣傳","createTime":"2019-07-27T05:34:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T05:43:32.000Z","uid":44557,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9a2802a44af20ade47f310913125bd7c7b0bcb37","tid":1370721,"uid":44557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:34:40.000Z","msg":"我們收到消息指於昨天（26/7）晚上九時許於香港國際機場，一名毛（譯音）姓男子懷疑襲擊一名連儂人牆的示威者。事主當時已即時報警並有警察到場調查。<br />\n<br />\n目前網上所流傳之片段是毛先生正離開機場前往巴士站時，位於機場客運一號大樓中間近往機鐵方向與途人發生拉扯，然而根據我們最新收到一段現場影片，可以清晰看到毛姓男子甫從抵港大堂B出閘，即衝向走道兩方的示威者，並粗暴地搶下示威標語。 另外有多名在場人士指出，及後毛姓男子開始將在場人仕手上的標語、傳單及牆上單張撕下並用力拍落地上，更用手及身體推撞黑衫人士及遊客。<br />\n<br />\n由於當時事主已報警，途人才會一直追趕該男子要求留下協助調查，即網上流傳影片內所呈現的片段。我們已經向警民關係科查詢，如有進一步消息，將盡快通知各位。此外亦希望各位現場朋友翻查當日所拍的影片，如與本案案情有關，請盡快和我們聯絡。謝謝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FXRBweo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFXRBweo.gif&h=8350e16b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/nqjsz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fnqjsz&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd0YZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=9d9bf571\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/nqjsz</a><br />\n<br />\n有任何消息請連絡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e3aab11d52298f774922775a8d801bf72fdad6","tid":1370721,"uid":44557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6346e9e6421e84e77b207caa73bc6703f8db74be","tid":1370721,"uid":44557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b2787953050c4bf96994d7240c2eaa4372e9ada","tid":1370721,"uid":152269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7450446ce7bc681446780a0c41f3727648b53c5","tid":1370721,"uid":276514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ee929888b04f207103183623c0d1efec0e0c29","tid":1370721,"uid":89862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:41:44.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"84ce160c7fe7edd9e995dd758b872d71d4487e86","tid":1370721,"uid":38139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:43:32.000Z","msg":"幾段影片最大問題，係有人不斷<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勁大聲屌個阿伯</span></span></strong><br />\n佢個樣又扮哂無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">無人打佢</span></span></strong><br />\n但影出黎唔好睇，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">希望手足注意下</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">(明白手足想保護大家既心理）<br />\n(不割蓆不分化）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外仆街陳怡已經扮嘢9up佢係教授呃支持<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EGY8njn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEGY8njn.png&h=ddbef51d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟做既簡單對比圖：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xDTkdre.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%